spec: asyncio_extra115
version: ">=3.11"
backend: python_module(asyncio)

docs: https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio-task.html

provenance:
  derived_from:
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio-task.html — Python asyncio task documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source: Lib/asyncio/taskgroups.py"
  notes:
    - "This spec extends asyncio_extra114.zspec.zsdl."
    - "This spec covers: wave 255 theme — asyncio.TaskGroup class method qualnames and co_qualname attributes (Python 3.11+) not covered in extra68-extra114. Prior specs covered: TaskGroup.__name__, __qualname__, __module__, __mro__.__len__(), __bases__[0].__name__, __dict__ membership. NOT previously covered: method qualname strings and co_qualname values. NEW in extra115: TaskGroup.create_task.__qualname__=='TaskGroup.create_task' (len=21, longest); TaskGroup.__aenter__.__qualname__=='TaskGroup.__aenter__' (len=20); TaskGroup.__aexit__.__qualname__=='TaskGroup.__aexit__' (len=19); TaskGroup.__init__.__qualname__=='TaskGroup.__init__' (len=18, shortest); and their co_qualname values (Python 3.11+) which match __qualname__; co_argcount: __init__=1 (self only), __aenter__=1 (self only), create_task=2 (self and coro), __aexit__=4 (self + exc_type + exc_val + exc_tb). TaskGroup.__module__.__len__()==18 ('asyncio.taskgroups'=18). All verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.TaskGroup.create_task.__qualname__ == 'TaskGroup.create_task' (len=21: 'TaskGroup.'=10+'create_task'=11=21; longest method qualname in spec). create_task accepts a coroutine and wraps it in a Task; the task is tracked by the TaskGroup and any exceptions propagate through the group. co_argcount=2 (self and coro; name and context are keyword-only, not counted in co_argcount). Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.TaskGroup.__aexit__.__qualname__ == 'TaskGroup.__aexit__' (len=19: 'TaskGroup.'=10+'__aexit__'=9=19). co_argcount=4 (self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb — standard async context manager exit signature); compare: __aenter__ co_argcount=1 (self only). Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.TaskGroup.__module__ == 'asyncio.taskgroups' (len=18: 'asyncio.taskgroups'=18). Coincidence: TaskGroup.__module__.__len__()==18 equals TaskGroup.__aenter__.__qualname__.__len__()==... wait: __aenter__.__qualname__.__len__()==20, not 18. TaskGroup.__init__.__qualname__.__len__()==18 coincidentally equals TaskGroup.__module__.__len__()==18. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
  created_at: "2026-04-11T00:00:00Z"

error_model: python_exceptions

