invariant asyncio_extra115.TaskGroup_create_task_qualname_len_21:
  description: "asyncio.TaskGroup.create_task.__qualname__.__len__() == 21 — 'TaskGroup.create_task' = 'TaskGroup.'=10 + 'create_task'=11 = 21; this is the longest method qualname in this spec; asyncio.TaskGroup.create_task.__qualname__.__eq__('TaskGroup.create_task')==True; asyncio.TaskGroup.create_task.__code__.co_qualname.__eq__('TaskGroup.create_task')==True (Python 3.11+, matches __qualname__); asyncio.TaskGroup.create_task.__code__.co_argcount==2 (self and coro; name and context parameters are keyword-only so they are not counted in co_argcount); asyncio.TaskGroup.create_task.__code__.co_name=='create_task' (len=11); compare qualname lengths: __init__=18 (shortest) < __aexit__=19 < __aenter__=20 < create_task=21 (longest); 'create_task'=11 chars is the longest method name in spec; first standalone TaskGroup.create_task qualname length invariant; wave 255; verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  category: code_attrs
  kind: python_call_eq
